Cost-Effectiveness of Erythropoietin in Traumatic Brain Injury: A Multinational 
Trial-Based Economic Analysis.

Knott RJ(1), Harris A(1), Higgins A(2), Nichol A(2)(3)(4), French C(5)(6), 
