Primary Results from SAUL, a Multinational Single-arm Safety Study of 
Atezolizumab Therapy for Locally Advanced or Metastatic Urothelial or 
Nonurothelial Carcinoma of the Urinary Tract.

Sternberg CN(1), Loriot Y(2), James N(3), Choy E(4), Castellano D(5), Lopez-Rios 
